Package com.conichi.sdk.beaconkit.scanner.internal

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CNIBeaconsListener
    Internal listener for beacon discovery and region recognition logic
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CNIAltBeaconRangeNotifier
    Internal class that receives beacon ranging notifications
    CNIAltBeaconWrapper
    CNIAltBeaconWrapper wraps AltBeacon library classes and allows to start/stop ranging process.
    CNIBeaconProcessor  
    CNIDefaultScanner
    CNIScanner implementation which uses CNIAltBeaconWrapper as a scanning tool and also depends on the Precondition object
    CNIEmptyScanner
    Stub implementation which throws UnsupportedOperationException when CNIEmptyScanner.startScanning() or CNIEmptyScanner.stopScanning() called
    CNIRegionCallback
    Processes leaving/discovering events for current region.
    CNIScannerFactory
    CNIScanController factory
    CNITransitionCallback
    Processes callback from different location venue/reegion changes.
    CNIVenueCallback
    Processes leaving/discovering event for current venue
    ScanningAwareConnectionListener
    Implementation of ConnectionListener which controls the ranging process depending on the current connection state.
